task.summary: Fixed bug where menuitem wouldn't initialize if not in root of menu.
Fixed bug with tree being invalidated when calling parseDOM twice.
Fixed bug where menu position wouldn't be inherited.
Fixed close on select not closing root context menu.
Added context menu positioner factory. Delay is now inherited. Moved logic from component register to constructor.
Moved component registration function into loaders file.
Refactored vectors into it's own directory.
Added test for x and y intersect amount when deciding which placement to use when out of bounds.
Added arrow class and connected to overlay.
Fix bug where overlay didn't account for arrow padding.
Made animation fx immutable and added the Promise interface.
Animation now reposition on every frame.
position was refactored to be a "protected" method.
Added fade in and out and compound animations.

Fixed bug with tooltip following mouse position. Fixed issue with ie not running animations Added custom event polyfill. Added scrollX and scrollY polyfill. Switched usages of scrollX and scrollY to pageXOffset and pageYOffset for better browser compatibility. Rect.translate method can now take an array of [x, y] coordinants.
Fixed import and css overflow error with panes.
Added SideMenu class. Fixed subclass directly referencing private properties.
Moved menu rendering out of render function to constructor.
Removed render method and fixed bug with menuitems not being registered in select menu.
Removed console logs and dead code.
Added test for delegating drag to child items.
